<p class="text-justify">
                <p> The festival is being organised as a part of 10 days Manipur Sangai Festival which is underway at Imphal.The three-day festival includes camping, local food stalls,  flower and vegetable stalls, cherry tree lightings, competition & exhibition, etc. Cherry Blossom is now a part of the Sangai Festival, the festival we will showcase the scenic beauty, landscapes of Manipur, besides the diverse culture and traditions of the Manipuri people.the festival is not just a simple festival, but will bind the hearts of the people of Manipur apart from promoting and encouraging the idea of oneness. Manipur Cherry Blossom Festival was held under the aegis of Mao Flower Growers’ Association and Institute of Bio-resources and Sustainable Development, a central institute in Manipur at Kayinu Village, Mao Gate</p>

